e field k, which can be embedded into\nthe complex numbers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 May 2004 13:41:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 May 2004 08:55:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 May 2004 11:45:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 May 2004 15:03:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
